      <h2>We’re here to help.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq reveal">
      <details class="acc" open>
        <summary>When will I feel something? <span class="pm" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <p>NAD⁺ replenishment is gradual — NMN+ isn’t formulated as a quick fix. In published human studies, supplemental NMN has been reported to raise blood NAD⁺ levels* — but those are studies of NMN generally, not of this product, and individual results are not established. Consistency matters more than timing — most people evaluate effects after 4–8 weeks.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="acc">
        <summary>How do I take NMN+? <span class="pm" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <p>Two capsules daily, ideally in the morning, with or without food. Consistency matters more than timing — NAD⁺ replenishment is a gradual process, so a steady daily habit beats perfect scheduling.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="acc">
        <summary>What’s actually in it? <span class="pm" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <p>NMN (nicotinamide mononucleotide), trans-resveratrol, quercetin, the active forms of vitamins B6, B12 and folate, and BioPerine black-pepper extract — in a plant-based HPMC capsule. Every dose is printed in full on the label, and the other ingredients (microcrystalline cellulose, magnesium stearate, silicon dioxide, and the vegetable capsule) are disclosed too. No proprietary blends. The exact milligrams are in the formula table above and on each batch’s <a href="/pages/lab-reports">Certificate of Analysis</a>.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "When will I feel something?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "NAD⁺ replenishment is gradual — NMN+ isn't formulated as a quick fix. In published human studies, supplemental NMN has been reported to raise blood NAD⁺ levels, but those are studies of NMN generally, not of this product, and individual results are not established. Consistency matters more than timing — most people evaluate effects after 4–8 weeks." } },
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "How do I take NMN+?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Two capsules daily, ideally in the morning, with or without food. Consistency matters more than timing — NAD⁺ replenishment is a gradual process, so a steady daily habit beats perfect scheduling." } },
    { "@type": "Question", "name": "What's actually in NMN+?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "NMN (nicotinamide mononucleotide), trans-resveratrol, quercetin, the active forms of vitamins B6, B12 and folate, and BioPerine black-pepper extract — in a plant-based HPMC capsule. Every dose is printed in full on the label, and the other ingredients are disclosed too. No proprietary blends." } }
  ]
}
</script>

<!-- ============ CLOSING CTA (green) ============ -->
<section class="band green">
  <div class="wrap closing reveal">
    <h2>Give your cells back what <em>time takes away.</em></h2>
    <p>NMN+ · 60 capsules · a 1-month supply.</p>
    {%- if has_product -%}
      <product-form-component
        id="nmn-pf-closing"
        data-section-id="{{ section.id }}"
        data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
        data-product-url="{{ product.url }}"
        on:submit="/handleSubmit"
        data-quantity-default="1"
      >
        <div class="visually-hidden" aria-live="assertive" role="status" aria-atomic="true" ref="liveRegion"></div>
        {%- form 'product', product, id: 'nmn-atc-closing', data-type: 'add-to-cart-form', class: 'nmn-form' -%}
          <input type="hidden" name="id" ref="variantId" value="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}">
          <span class="product-form-text__error hidden" ref="addToCartTextError"></span>
          <add-to-cart-component ref="addToCartButtonContainer" data-add-to-cart-animation="false">
            <button type="submit" name="add" class="cta" ref="addToCartButton" on:click="/handleClick"{% unless product.available %} disabled{% endunless %}>
              {% if product.available %}Add to Cart — {{ product.price | money }}{% else %}Sold Out{% endif %}
            </button>
          </add-to-cart-component>
        {%- endform -%}
      </product-form-component>
    {%- else -%}
      <a href="#nmn-top" class="cta">Add to Cart</a>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</section>

