  <div class="wrap">
    <p>*These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Where research is referenced, it refers to studies of NMN and its cofactors in general, not to this specific product.</p>
  </div>
